      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><strong>RenderManStudio_Layout_v01.hip</strong><br/><br/>This scene is where the layout magic happens.  <br/><br/>The <em>$HIP/usd/Assembly/RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.usda </em>file is referenced and then using both the <em>setvariant </em>and <em>edit </em>nodes, the assets are laid out and the scene formed.  <br/><br/>Feel free to drop a camera here as well, but don't forget to add a <em>layerbreak </em>node if you don't want that layout camera to be saved</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642665/RenderManStudio_Layout_ScreenShot_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104938&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642665/RenderManStudio_Layout_ScreenShot_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433104938&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642679\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Layout_ScreenShot_Solaris.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642665\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"63ae88f1-f5e1-4deb-9f78-940366f70da4\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>Once happy with the layout, use the <em>usd_Layout</em> USD rop to save out the layout file <em>$HIP/usd/Layout/RenderManStudio_Layout_v1.usda - </em>ready to be loaded in the next and final stage -<a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/display/RFH25/Lighting+Stage\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Lighting, FX, and Rendering !! </a><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></p>"
    }
